{
  "stem": "12413.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "What's really painful to me, today, when I'm talking about these crucial moments of the liberation, when American armies-- the Third Army-- under General Patton, the Seventh Army, the First Army, the Sixth Armored division-- were three miles from Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were patrols moving all around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't know then, but I knew later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Under the-- their noses, the Germans succeeded to take out the people, the inmates, half-dead, to kill them, in the final demise of the Third Reich.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I'm not trying to accuse no one.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There is no hatred in my heart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There is a lot of pain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Especially the moment that I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "When I left the hospital, on April 11th, 1945, pleading with the doctor to stay another few hours.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because the retreat was in progress from 11 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was after 11:00.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I read this in on April 22, 1985, the retreat of the German from Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He said no, you are in good shape.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You can walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "In a few hours, maybe an hour, the American forces will be here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I walked, and I saw the German SS by hundreds, armed, outside the barbed wire, retreating in disarray, frightened.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was walking toward the main gate to look for my brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We gave a vow to each other that after the liberation, or at the liberation movement, we will search-- we'll look for each other among, you know, thousand, thousands of inmates.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I didn't found him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Adjacent to the gates, hundreds of bodies were laying on the ground-- some in the last moment of their agony.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Voices-- [NON-ENGLISH]-- 'Listen, God of Israel!' [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Some stretching their hands for help, some dead, some covered in blankets, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] dead.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
